column5: Went back up this time with 9 guys at two outpost camps. Couldn't count the number of walleye this time but we'll well over 500. Great fish fry and fun was had by all. Biggest was 5lbs but lots of 2 and three pounders
Awesome! And how were the bugs?Â  Nothing like earlier, I imagine? Doug
